response.overview: Celebrating a decade of chart-topping success, this collection showcases Australian singer-songwriter Tina Arena performing her most beloved hits from 1994 to 2004. Known for her powerful voice and emotive delivery, Arena captivates audiences with classics such as Chains, Burn, Wasn’t It Good, and Sorrento Moon. Blending pop, ballads, and soulful performances, this release captures the artistry and versatility that have made her one of Australia’s most enduring and internationally acclaimed artists.
response.title: Tina Arena - Greatest Hits 1994-2004
